    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hullbreaker</strong> is a multiplayer action roguelike that combines naval warfare with deckbuilding roguelike elements. Customize your ship with different weapons to forge your own vessel to take on other players by clashing on the high seas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MIX-AND-MATCH DIFFERENT UPGRADE COMBINATIONS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093700/extras/e7b093562e4551c085312ac73f29ba91.poster.avif?t=1759257845\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093700/extras/e7b093562e4551c085312ac73f29ba91.webm?t=1759257845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093700/extras/e7b093562e4551c085312ac73f29ba91.mp4?t=1759257845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Apply weapons to your ship to give yourself a peg leg up over other captains. Some of the armaments include cannons and different shot types, long-range mortars, and deadly trap barrels. With upgrades able to boost stats and give unique effects to each one the possibilities are endless for customization!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BECOME THE PIRATE KING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093700/extras/310a2c1fe7edac152087de876e326837.poster.avif?t=1759257845\" width=608 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093700/extras/310a2c1fe7edac152087de876e326837.webm?t=1759257845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093700/extras/310a2c1fe7edac152087de876e326837.mp4?t=1759257845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle up to 4 other players in a dynamic round based naval experience and utilize your ship to the fullest extent to best other captains. Create unique strategies with your ship and plan out how to counter your foes in the deadly arena. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DYNAMIC ENVIROMENT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093700/extras/dbf1cf30694eaa0d263622737f4adcc1.poster.avif?t=1759257845\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093700/extras/dbf1cf30694eaa0d263622737f4adcc1.webm?t=1759257845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093700/extras/dbf1cf30694eaa0d263622737f4adcc1.mp4?t=1759257845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The sea is vast and ever-changing, ensuring that each battle is a unique experience. Experience a dynamic realistic ocean simulation that challenges your abilities at the helm with many different weather effects to watch out for like strong gales, whirlpools, hurricanes, and even volcano eruptions! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CREATE YOUR OWN FLAG!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093700/extras/ce156daf920e19be1600f48215892992.poster.avif?t=1759257845\" width=256 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093700/extras/ce156daf920e19be1600f48215892992.webm?t=1759257845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093700/extras/ce156daf920e19be1600f48215892992.mp4?t=1759257845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly your flag with pride! Aided by a custom drawing editor that takes your very own design and applies it to your ship in game. </p>",
